📋 Pain Point Analysis (4 Dimensions):

  A. Pain Points:
    1. Existing telematics data models cannot support ML-enabled product requirements, blocking new feature development
    2. Platform architectural gaps preventing launch of ML-driven telematics products
    3. Telematics data processing infrastructure at capacity with 2.3M IoT devices generating trillions of annual data points
    4. Cross-team integration problems when telematics data flows to downstream products (Video Safety, Equipment Monitoring, Apps)
    5. Production system stability issues requiring dedicated tech lead ownership

  B. Strategic Needs:
    1. Launch ML-enabled telematics products to differentiate in competitive IoT market post-IPO
    2. Redesign core data platform to support 10x IoT device growth trajectory
    3. Establish reusable data abstractions across Video Safety, Telematics, Equipment Monitoring product suite
